{
  "stem": "9730.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You-- you learn how to extract certain information that-- that help you to put the pieces together.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the-- they were mainly the-- the battles of-- for those cities that I mentioned-- Angers-- well, then first the breakthrough in Saint-Lo, then Angers, then Reims, then Verdun.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and then, by-- by fall of '44, we were-- we had-- you know, I was with Patton's Third Army.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And incidentally, I met General Patton, and he even posed for me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- I took some pictures of him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I-- I chatted with him for a brief while.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was quite an experience.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we-- we actually came to a halt in the city of Metz, because we had run out of gas, and we had to wait because General Patton had gone so fast that some of the supplies couldn't keep up.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Also, there weren't enough of them, so we had to sort of regroup.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we spent a considerable amount of time in-- in the city of Metz.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, occasionally, he would-- he would come to visit, to-- to check on what was going on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And first of all, I can only say that he was one general that was in any battle, did not shirk danger.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He-- he was right there with the troops, which instilled a great deal of confidence in the troops, and even-- and despite his profanity and the kind of pep talks that he was so well known for, we sort of took that in almost in a humorous vein, and-- and the-- and the GIs had a lot of respect for him.",
      "word_count": 61
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some of the things that you've heard about him is that he-- he was a little bit vain, perhaps, and was always seeking glory.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
